26#ifndef LAFE_ERR_H
27#define LAFE_ERR_H
28
29#if defined(__GNUC__) && (__GNUC__ > 2 || \
30 (__GNUC__ == 2 && __GNUC_MINOR__ >= 5))
31#define __LA_DEAD __attribute__((__noreturn__))
32#else
33#define __LA_DEAD
34#endif
35
36#if defined(__GNUC__) && (__GNUC__ > 2 || \
37 (__GNUC__ == 2 && __GNUC_MINOR__ >= 7))
38#define __LA_PRINTFLIKE(f,a) __attribute__((__format__(__printf__, f, a)))
39#else
40#define __LA_PRINTFLIKE(f,a)
41#endif
42
43void lafe_warnc(int code, const char *fmt, ...) __LA_PRINTFLIKE(2, 3);
44void lafe_errc(int eval, int code, const char *fmt, ...) __LA_DEAD
45 __LA_PRINTFLIKE(3, 4);
46
47const char * lafe_getprogname(void);
48void lafe_setprogname(const char *name, const char *defaultname);
49
50#endif
